Interface IChangeEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IConcreteDomainChangeEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChangeEntry, ConceptConcreteDomainChangeEntry, RelationshipChangeEntry, RelationshipChangeEntryBase, RelationshipConcreteDomainChangeEntry

    public interface IChangeEntry
extends Serializable
    Common interface for all change entries reported in a reasoner change set.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ChangeConcept getDestination()
      Returns the concept to be displayed in the destination column, which is: the relationship destination concept for relationships; the relationship destination concept for relationship concrete domain members; null for concept concrete domain members.
      AbstractChangeEntry.Nature getNature() 
      ChangeConcept getSource()
      Returns the concept to be displayed in the source column, which is: the relationship source concept for relationships; the relationship source concept for relationship concrete domain members; the referenced concept for concept concrete domain members.
      ChangeConcept getType()
      Returns the concept to be displayed in the type column, which is: the relationship type concept for relationships; the relationship type concept for relationship concrete domain members; null for concept concrete domain members.
